Some of my recent projects

MERN Expense Tracker

An easy-to-use expense tracker to track your income and expenses where user can list their income or expenses and track their total balance, amount left, amount spent and checks their transaction details.

ReactJs and React Native Restaurant Website / Mobile App

A ReactJS restaurant website and mobile application with various sections as Menu, About Us, a Contact Us form page and a table reservation page and various preloading animations and gestures for UX enhancement.

An E-diary with login and OAuth.

A simple E-diary to keep your secrets and thoughts with login and OAuth authentication built with NodeJS, MongoDB, OAuth & Passport.js.

Online Face Recognition Attendance System (BE Group Project)

An application which automates the attendance marking system by monitoring and verifying student's face throughout the lecture. The application has a login system for students and teachers with necessary features.
